NHL ENTRY DRAFT
June 24, 2006
Niklas Backstrom
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT







 Q.  How do you feel now? 
 NICKLAS BACKSTROM:  I feel good, watching the club and some other players, I'm very happy. 

 Q.  How do you feel about playing with Alex Ovechkin in the near future? 
 NICKLAS BACKSTROM:  If I'm good enough to play in the NHL and play with him, I'll be very happy.  He's very good. 

 Q.  What are your thoughts on playing in Sweden in 2006/2007 or coming over to the United States and playing in North America? 
 NICKLAS BACKSTROM:  I don't know yet.  I think I'll make the decision after some weeks.  I don't know yet.  But make NHL, I don't know. 

